{"total":13,"pageSize":10,"pageCount":2,"data":[{"title":"Newbie_calculations","slug":"XCTF Newbie_calculations","date":"2021-01-09T06:10:47.440Z","updated":"2021-01-09T06:12:46.471Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/XCTF Newbie_calculations.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210109140716669.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center","content":"<p><a href=\"https://adworld.xctf.org.cn/task/answer?type=reverse&number=4&grade=1&id=4973&page=2\">Newbie_calculations</a></p>\n<p>得到的32位exe文件，使用ida分析，发现程序一直再调用三个程序，但是运行程序却没有结果</p>\n<p>于是打开三个程序进行分析，发现程序依次进行的对应的为加减乘三种运算，但是在进行运算时，程序时进行的+1的操作，借助有符号数的边界进行。</p>\n<p>经过适当的修改之后，就可以得到main（）的功能<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210109140716669.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>其中v120为一个被初始化为1 的数组，也是最后的结果数组，分析整个程序之后，就可以得到flag</p>\n","text":"Newbie_calculations得到的32位exe文件，使用ida分析，发现程序一直再调用三个程序，但是运行程序却没有结果于是打开三个程序进行分析，发现程序依次进行的对应的为加减乘三种运算，但是在进行运算时，程序时进行的+1的操作，借助有符号数的边界进行。经过适当的修改之后","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"oldDriver","slug":"XCTF oldDriver","date":"2021-01-09T03:49:00.549Z","updated":"2021-01-09T06:12:45.497Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/XCTF oldDriver.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://adworld.xctf.org.cn/task/answer?type=crypto&number=5&grade=1&id=4672&page=1\">oldDriver</a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>[{“c”: 7366067574741171461722065133242916080495505913663250330082747465383676893970411476550748394841437418105312353971095003424322679616940371123028982189502042, “e”: 10, “n”: 2516250705233971442183968887373459617775112403672383100330095976113781149071520574294173840654815024086177930178413365216590822791741548313758538898